{"tid":718431,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友 我當你一世朋友","createTime":"2018-06-26T19:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T02:24:57.000Z","uid":68697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"501f020de165f0208f218c9bd387692cd2bb5e36","tid":718431,"uid":68697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T19:14:55.000Z","msg":"最近份工比人炒左<br />\n其實都知自己衰d咩<br />\n都明白唔低可憐<br />\n<br />\n自己係一個好負面既人<br />\n交心既朋友真係無咩<br />\n<br />\n一個識左十幾年既朋友<br />\n突然之間無再理過我<br />\n到今日我好想知點解<br />\n就去問<br />\n<br />\n朋友一下子將咁多年既心結講左出尼<br />\n我其實都知做唔到朋友架喇<br />\n<br />\n佢係我既其中一個支柱<br />\n我宜家都唔知可以同邊個講..<br />\n<br />\n覺得人生好失敗"},{"pid":"bb005ed9e24f54dc05c29533a9ecccc623a8f442","tid":718431,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T19:17:35.000Z","msg":"尼你老母<br />\n抵撚死"},{"pid":"6398756d1dea961ad6618776c3d3dce35b6cc947","tid":718431,"uid":170867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T19:17:49.000Z","msg":"實實在在踏入過我宇宙<br />\n即使相處到有個裂口<br />\n命運決定了以後再沒法聚頭<br />\n但說過去卻那樣厚"},{"pid":"b536ebf2e45a43af6e9192ab8f55313132aced56","tid":718431,"uid":68697,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bb005ed9e24f54dc05c29533a9ecccc623a8f442","tid":718431,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T19:17:35.000Z","msg":"尼你老母<br />\n抵撚死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T19:18:47.000Z","msg":"應該點打...<br />\nsorry..<br />\n係泥定咩"},{"pid":"b486538a9c24f587f094a3a9eac50e82e20e6fee","tid":718431,"uid":68697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b536ebf2e45a43af6e9192ab8f55313132aced56","tid":718431,"uid":68697,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bb005ed9e24f54dc05c29533a9ecccc623a8f442","tid":718431,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T19:17:35.000Z","msg":"尼你老母<br />\n抵撚死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T19:18:47.000Z","msg":"應該點打...<br />\nsorry..<br />\n係泥定咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T19:19:24.000